reviewText: Exactly as shown in pictures. Fast delivery

My children love Gina! they get to sing, dance and most importantly, learn! It showcases family values through song. It says for ages 2-6, but my 1 year old enjoys it too, for entertainment purposes only. But, in the future, will learn so much from it as well. This show has all kinds of characters that kids will just love. I highly recommend Gina D's Kids Club. :)
